title: Sample Book, Cotton Prints Samples, 1845–60
dimensions:
H x W x D: 32.7 x 38.1 x 4.5 cm (12 7/8 in. x 15 in. x 1 3/4 in.)
130 pages
description: Blue cloth bound volume of 338 samples of printed cotton. Title page has three labels pasted on it. Each pattern is numbered. Most designs form stripes, either floral or geometrical or combinations of both.
